Chelsea striker Didier Drogba has spoken of his delight after John Terry signed a one-year contract extension with the Blues.

The Chelsea skipper has signed on until the end of the 2015-16 campaign and Drogba believes the the new contract is fully deserved. 

Speaking to the official Chelsea website, Drogba said: 'When you see the way he has performed and that the manager is happy with him. 

